              DIR-FILE; don't insert any new entries.

       ----ddeessccrriippttiioonn=_T_E_X_T
              the description of the entry is TEXT; used with the
              ----nnaammee option to become synonymous with the ----eennttrryy
              option.

       ----ddiirr--ffiillee=_N_A_M_E
              specify  file  name of Info directory file; equiva-
              lent to using the DIR-FILE argument.

